    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Featuring a nail file and nail cleaner, knife blade, scissors and keyring, this ASR Outdoor mini pocket knife is ready for adventure! Great for camping, to carry as an EDC multitool, to include with a bug out bag, survival gear or an emergency preparedness kit, this little pocket knife does it all. Compact and lightweight, the multitool pocket knife weights under a pound and measures just 2.25 inches when closed. Whether you’re fishing, hunting, backpacking, camping or prepping gear for an outdoor survival or emergency preparedness kit, include this mini ASR Outdoor pocket knife to have alongside you on your next outdoor excursion; each tool locks in place for consistent, efficient and reliable performance, and it will never ask you to sacrifice on weight or space</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Multifunctional EDC Small Pocket Knife Multi Tool (5 Colors)</h2>\n  <p>Featuring a nail file and nail cleaner, knife blade, scissors and keyring, this ASR Outdoor mini pocket knife is ready for adventure! Great for camping, to carry as an EDC multitool, to include with a bug out bag, survival gear or an emergency preparedness kit, this little pocket knife does it all.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>3 in 1 SMALL EDC POCKET KNIFE:</strong> Featuring a nail file, knife blade, scissors and keyring, this ASR Outdoor mini pocket knife is ready for adventure; great for camping and every day carry on your key ring</li>\n    <li><strong>COMPACT DESIGN:</strong> Small pocket knife is just 2.25 inches overall when closed; super lightweight you&#039;ll never sacrifice on space or weight</li>\n    <li><strong>TASK READY:</strong> Whether you’re fishing, hunting, backpacking, camping or prepping gear for an outdoor survival or emergency preparedness kit, this mini ASR Outdoor pocket knife is a great holiday gift idea for mens stocking stuffers</li>\n    <li><strong>KEYCHAIN POCKET KNIFE:</strong> With an included keychain ring incorporated into the design, you can attach the mini pocket knife multitool to just about anything you need: backpack, camping gear, keys and much more</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Blade Length: 1.5 inch; Closed Length: 2.25 inch; Open Length: 5.5 inch; Available Colors: Black, Green, Purple, Blue or Red; Material: Plastic, Metal; No assembly required</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/hobby_knives/ASR_Outdoor_Multifunctional_EDC_Small_Pocket_Knife_Multi_Tool_Black_PL.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Featuring a nail file and nail cleaner, knife blade, scissors and keyring, this ASR Outdoor mini pocket knife is ready for adventure\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASR61PKN</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058485243</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 2.25 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Compact and lightweight, the multitool pocket knife weights under a pound and measures just 2.25 inches when closed. Whether you’re fishing, hunting, backpacking, camping or prepping gear for an outdoor survival or emergency preparedness kit, include this mini ASR Outdoor pocket knife to have alongside you on your next outdoor excursion; each tool locks in place for consistent, efficient and reliable performance, and it will never ask you to sacrifice on weight or space.</p>\n  <p>With the included keychain ring incorporated into the design, you can attach the pocket knife multitool to just about anything you need: backpack, wallet, belt loop camping gear and much more, depending on where work or your next camping trip or hike takes you.</p>\n  <p>Available Colors: Black, Green, Blue or Red</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Featuring a nail file and nail cleaner, knife blade, scissors and keyring, this ASR Outdoor mini pocket knife is ready for adventure! Great for camping, to carry as an EDC multitool, to include with a bug out bag, survival gear or an emergency preparedness kit, this little pocket knife does it all. Compact and lightweight, the multitool pocket knife weights under a pound and measures just 2.25 inches when closed. Whether you’re fishing, hunting, backpacking, camping or prepping gear for an outdoor survival or emergency preparedness kit, include this mini ASR Outdoor pocket knife to have alongside you on your next outdoor excursion; each tool locks in place for consistent, efficient and reliable performance, and it will never ask you to sacrifice on weight or space.",
